reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WORTH THE MONEY I PROMISE
reviews.reviewText: The utensils are sturdy and appropriately sharp, including the knife.The presentation is great.The napkin is just WOW. very thick and nice. You will really only need one napkin for dinner. These were definitely exceptional.Definitely buying for my next event that includes disposable cutlery. Saved me so much time and worry. Worth every penny.
